platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This writing app is designed to let you type without distraction. Key features weve come to depend on include the customisable keyboard, iCloud sync and its streamlined interface for easy document preview and access.

When we want to hunker down and type without distraction, one of our favorite resources is iA Writer. Substantially updated since its initial release, this writing app offers a customizable keyboard, selective text highlighting, iCloud sync, and many other features weve come to depend on. Plus, a streamlined interface lets you simply swipe left to preview a document and swipe right to access your library. The entire experience is designed to be quick and easy so you can focus on your work.
